body: Zilong, I apologize for the late response.  The csv lighting schedules were not having an effect because of a bug that I just fixed: [https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/commit/43c2587024a7e7a...](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/commit/43c2587024a7e7a739cdfc6d02eb32cf06a10480) [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/Wui*gYiAaOoV3QJiOwImiPSc6F19iX8im8sEEHKINPaWuzj60KtiTrIj2ZvZ8ka4spGGpO1M-LoJfdhdz0pQNZ-sA7Ve9GWC/FixedCSVLighting.JPG) Update your components and you should see that you now get non-zero lighting. -Chris
